1
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure it doesn't look odd?</font>

2
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all, Kana-chan.</font>

3
00:00:07,950 --> 00:00:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say you look better than most.</font>

4
00:00:11,150 --> 00:00:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Some people say foreigners 
don't suit yukata one bit,</i></font>

5
00:00:14,410 --> 00:00:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but maybe his Japanese half or DNA
 is making all the difference?</i></font>

6
00:00:18,190 --> 00:00:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Mom?</font>

7
00:00:19,570 --> 00:00:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me what you think
of my yukata.</font>

8
00:00:21,950 --> 00:00:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course, I think 
you look cute, too, Ren-chan.</font>

9
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not even looking!</font>

10
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking forward to 
my first Japanese fireworks display.</font>

11
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must have 
fireworks in England.</font>

12
00:00:34,490 --> 00:00:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure.</font>

13
00:00:35,530 --> 00:00:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In particular, I remember my mum taking
me out in London on Guy Fawkes Night.</font>

14
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, really?</font>

15
00:00:46,670 --> 00:00:48,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a request, Ren.</font>

16
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why are you being so formal?</font>

17
00:00:51,870 --> 00:00:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to take a picture of you.</font>

18
00:00:55,370 --> 00:00:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A picture? Of me in my yukata?</font>

19
00:00:58,790 --> 00:01:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a no, then?</font>

20
00:01:01,780 --> 00:01:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I didn't say that.</font>

21
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Ren.</font>

22
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's what you really want, 
take as many as you like.</font>

23
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

24
00:01:12,210 --> 00:01:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, I know I looked ugly 
in that one. Take another!</font>

25
00:01:16,020 --> 00:01:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. You're the cutest 
in the world, Ren.</font>

26
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I seriously have no idea 
what English guys consider cute.</i></font>

27
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#ff060f">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></font></b></font>

28
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial">Sparks Fly</font></b></font>

29
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we're taking pictures, 
let's get one of both of us in our yukatas.</font>

30
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I ask someone to take it for us?</font>

31
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea.</font>

32
00:01:45,030 --> 00:01:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

33
00:01:57,070 --> 00:02:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. It's the Enoshima 
fireworks festival today.</font>

34
00:02:01,270 --> 00:02:05,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. Ren and Kana-chan 
looked thrilled to be going out in yukata.</font>

35
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were like two peas in a pod.</font>

36
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:12,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, they seem 
like real siblings to me.</font>

37
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And maybe someday...</font>

38
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I see those fireworks,</font>

39
00:02:19,850 --> 00:02:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it reminds me summer's ending,
 and that makes me a little sad.</font>

40
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I read somewhere that getting 
sentimental over the end of summer</font>

41
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is unique to Japan.</font>

42
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Why would that be?</font>

43
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Japan apparently has the richest
four seasons in the whole world.</font>

44
00:02:46,290 --> 00:02:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman">Amazing.</font></font>

45
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen such 
impressive fireworks before.</font>

46
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I love that firework smell.</i></font>

47
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is beautiful, Ren.</font>

48
00:02:58,010 --> 00:03:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kanata's having such a good time.
 I'm so glad I invited him.</i></font>

49
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So much has happened,
 both happy and sad.</i></font>

50
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This summer really has been jam-packed.</i></font>

51
00:03:12,450 --> 00:03:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Goodbye, my 17th summer.</i></font>

52
00:03:16,050 --> 00:03:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wasn't lonely at all this year,
 thanks to Kanata.</i></font>

53
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope I can spend next year with him, too.
 And even more after that.</i></font>

54
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if, little by little, 
I'm starting to want more and more.</i></font>

55
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Impressive.</i></font>

56
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold up a sec! 
Don't forget our promise!</font>

57
00:03:46,650 --> 00:03:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We said no attacking corners
 until I get out, Kanata!</font>

58
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman">Yes, of course.</font></font>

59
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><font face="Times New Roman">Amazing, Mr. Okuyama. <font face="Trebuchet MS">I'm shocked 
at how much the 86 has evolved.</font></font></i></font>

60
00:03:58,070 --> 00:04:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too fast! Too fast! 
Even this is too fast!</font>

61
00:04:04,210 --> 00:04:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I'm off.</font>

62
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you can go all out now.</font>

63
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even compared to the upgrades for the 
third race at Manazuru, I can feel changes.</i></font>

64
00:04:22,150 --> 00:04:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got more downforce.</i></font>

65
00:04:23,970 --> 00:04:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Going over bumps before, 
I'd have to lift off to keep control.</i></font>

66
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now, with the air pushing the car down 
into the road, I can go full throttle.</i></font>

67
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He said he didn't change 
the turbo levels,</i></font>

68
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the engine's clearly revving
much sharper than before.</i></font>

69
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You've put me in a spot 
of bother, Mr. Okuyama.</i></font>

70
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With a car like this, 
I won't be able to make any excuses.</i></font>

71
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nozomi and Kakeru?</i></font>

72
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, hey, it's Kanata.</i></font>

73
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kanata! Over here!</font>

74
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman">Hi, Nozomi.</font></font>

75
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me introduce you. 
This is my mechanic, Yamatani-kun.</font>

76
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello there.</font>

77
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure.</font>

78
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my mechanic, Ogata-san.</font>

79
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's also the 86's owner.</font>

80
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there.</font>

81
00:05:29,890 --> 00:05:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The 86 is starting to look good out there.</font>

82
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The aero tweaks are paying dividends,
but just its whole aura is different now.</font>

83
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Call it my mechanic instincts.</font>

84
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you see, we've got 
this really talented advisor.</font>

85
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's embarrassing to admit, 
but I've let him make most of the calls.</font>

86
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, by the way, we came for a test run
yesterday and saw the 4 car.</font>

87
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sawatari Koki's upgraded his ride, too.</font>

88
00:05:57,430 --> 00:06:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are reports Michael 
Beckenbauer has a new car, too.</font>

89
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's already at it.</font>

90
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Double Lane might as well have started.
Sparks are already flying.</font>

91
00:06:08,650 --> 00:06:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about your car?</font>

92
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fiddled with the software. 
Gave it a power boost, too.</font>

93
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know my bro's tweaked 
the suspension of his Lotus.</font>

94
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want it too rigid
 for Double Lane.</font>

95
00:06:18,610 --> 00:06:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not with <i>that</i> road feature.</font>

96
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:24,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bro's all worked up.
He was in the car a lot yesterday.</font>

97
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He kinda sucks, so it takes him
a while to master tracks.</font>

98
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike me, he's got 
no natural sense for it.</font>

99
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kind of talk is why 
you two are always fighting.</font>

100
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For someone like me
 who prefers a responsive car,</i></font>

101
00:06:42,990 --> 00:06:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it's gonna take a while to get used
 to this kind of long stroke.</i></font>

102
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I think I'm finally 
getting the hang of it.</i></font>

103
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who's this?</i></font>

104
00:06:55,580 --> 00:06:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never seen that car before.</i></font>

105
00:06:57,810 --> 00:07:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since you're another English-made car, 
I'll show you some respect, Lotus.</i></font>

106
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I'll make it look good
 as I blow past you.</i></font>

107
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An Aston Martin, huh?</i></font>

108
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn. Talk about powerful.</i></font>

109
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That driver's really good.</i></font>

110
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From that honed technique,</i></font>

111
00:07:19,820 --> 00:07:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it seems like MFG's getting
 another new face with talent.</i></font>

112
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's September, but the sun's
showing no sign of letting up.</i></font>

113
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Out goes summer, in comes the high-speed
 brawl that is Seaside Double Lane.</i></font>

114
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've waited for this,
 and we're glad to bring it to you.</font>

115
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I really do mean that.</font>

116
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Tanaka Yoji on comms.</font>

117
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A lap around here
 is 21.7 km,</i></font>

118
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and the race will 
consist of six laps.</i></font>

119
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Heading north 
with Sagami Bay</i></font>

120
00:07:52,910 --> 00:07:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}on the right 
before doubling back,</i></font>

121
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}this course may seem
 relatively simple,</i></font>

122
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}but high average 
speeds will punish</i></font>

123
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}even a moment's
 carelessness.</i></font>

124
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's the first day of qualifying,</i></font>

125
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and we have one of this year's
 top three on track already.</i></font>

126
00:08:08,010 --> 00:08:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This driver has lots of fans,</i></font>

127
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and since his mid-season return, he's shown
incredible natural driving instincts.</i></font>

128
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In that dazzling French blue, 
it's the 4 car, driven by Sawatari Koki.</i></font>

129
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And he rockets away!</i></font>

130
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sawatari Koki's up already, huh?</i></font>

131
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter how you slice it, 
he's one of the favorites to win.</i></font>

132
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This timed lap was always
 gonna attract attention.</i></font>

133
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the time the 4 car sets will be the 
benchmark for the remaining seven days.</i></font>

134
00:08:44,130 --> 00:08:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm looking forward to this, A110S.</i></font>

135
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And Sawatari Koki is underway.</i></font>

136
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He already has an attention flag on him
 through this high-speed first sector.</i></font>

137
00:08:57,710 --> 00:09:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Since it's the first day, 
we have no real point of comparison.</i></font>

138
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's already setting better sector times
 than Akaba Kaito's course record...</font>

139
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}...from last season!</i></font>

140
00:09:12,650 --> 00:09:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And he clears the Jumping Spot!</i></font>

141
00:09:14,530 --> 00:09:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}His pace remains high,</i></font>

142
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and he's on course to beat the 
lap record by nearly two whole seconds!</i></font>

143
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must leave no room for excuses
 and push myself as hard as I can.</i></font>

144
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's my plan this time around.</i></font>

145
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:29,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Michael Beckenbauer. 
Kanata Rivington.</i></font>

146
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You'd better watch your backs.</i></font>

147
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And through the complicated 
residential area of Sector 3,</i></font>

148
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}he still has the attention flag.</i></font>

149
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}He's pushing right to the limit here!</i></font>

150
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And as he crosses the finish line,</i></font>

151
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}he smashes Akaba Kaito's previous 
course record by a good three seconds.</i></font>

152
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}If a driver's time from the first day
ends up being good enough for pole,</i></font>

153
00:09:59,450 --> 00:10:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}that'll be a first in the history of MFG!</i></font>

154
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sawatari Koki has put in 
a truly godly performance today!</i></font>

155
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}MF Ghost.</i></font>

156
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Traits of an only child: 
We don't mind being on our own."</font>

157
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"No. 2: We try to solve problems
 on our own without any help."</font>

158
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's all that?</font>

159
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:32,860
